ts/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<blockquote>海洋文明係唔需要搶正統。大陸文明嘅維生工具係土地，因此佔領農地就完全控制生產，成為霸主。另外，因為土地權係排他，所以大陸文明傾向視經濟為零和遊戲：對家多佔一塊田地，我方就少左一塊田地。儒家嘅「名不正，言不順」，都係依個世界觀嘅延伸，係大陸文明心態潛意識下搵野去佔領，認為佔領左所謂嘅正統，就會臣服四方。</blockquote>"},{"pid":"6cf2fc05c9e35846bf8b0a4ccb96441f2d729456","tid":359944,"uid":27630,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-15T02:43:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n佢做保險月入分分鐘唔過最低工資喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8725855f0ff4c5e79c911fe911cbf734e89f5c2c","tid":359944,"uid":27630,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-15T02:46:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n佢做保險月入分分鐘唔過最低工資喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"47262b26dfbc556f63f506078d9c66138e1afb7a","tid":359944,"uid":116443,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-15T02:46:35.000Z","msg":"日扑夜扑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"94386e9909a70e4cc1f18a822e50e8d3efcc5613","tid":359944,"uid":131064,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-15T03:11:57.000Z","msg":"梁應該炒散,之前見佢派傳單叫人搭高鐵,可能泊到好碼頭,遲下做高鐵管理層"}]}